pattern_2.text: I don't know factually what it is about but I did notice the numbers on the jerseys were all 17, 18, 19, 71, 81, 91. I also noticed that the colors of their jerseys had a pattern but I couldn't quite catch it. I'm not sure if the skin color of the players alternated perfectly but I noticed that the numbers, colors, and skin color were combined somewhat differently across individual pictures.
